{"tid":652820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東涌發現垃圾袋藏屍 警封現場調查","createTime":"2018-05-04T07:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T10:49:22.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"93d4de044b8260f27c932d6a94aab1411e4b3dcb","tid":652820,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T07:05:07.000Z","msg":"東涌暢連路一個工地，早上10時18分，警方接獲工人報案，指在上址發現一個黑色膠袋，內裏藏有異物感到可疑，於是報警。警方到場調查，剪開膠袋，發現藏有一具男屍，遂將封鎖範圍擴大至100米，並架起帳篷遮蓋屍體，鑑證科人員已到場搜證，正追查死者的身分及死因，新界南警區重案組人員已接手調查。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/JD967zXRGpq3htrbehgeVQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/919eca1e2003d831ee493993cdc699f7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FJD967zXRGpq3htrbehgeVQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F919eca1e2003d831ee493993cdc699f7&h=cb97e0ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9D%B1%E6%B6%8C%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E8%A2%8B%E8%97%8F%E5%B1%8D%E3%80%80%E8%AD%A6%E5%B0%81%E7%8F%BE%E5%A0%B4%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-042849955.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%259D%25B1%25E6%25B6%258C%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%259E%2583%25E5%259C%25BE%25E8%25A2%258B%25E8%2597%258F%25E5%25B1%258D%25E3%2580%2580%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25B0%2581%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5-042849955.html&d=VW6EldCff5cYGF6oeE%2BgtW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=bf7d1fde\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9D%B1%E6%B6%8C%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E8%A2%8B%E8%97%8F%E5%B1%8D%E3%80%80%E8%AD%A6%E5%B0%81%E7%8F%BE%E5%A0%B4%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-042849955.html</a>"},{"pid":"8b028e8a77b15189464da1ada7be076f52e0144c","tid":652820,"uid":111996,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-0